7
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,240
No.

8
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:56,880
No, no.

9
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,920
No, it's not like that, officer.

10
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:02,360
How do you have this?

11
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,080
I clearly remember I already...

12
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:06,280
Threw it away, right?

13
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,440
Just this one thing.

14
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,840
We can find it wherever you throw it.

15
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:20,579
You threw it in the trash can at the industrial park.

16
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,760
If we were a little later,

17
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:23,890
it would have been buried and cleared.

18
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:26,140
I can only say you were out of luck.

19
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,280
Tell the truth.

20
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:31,079
What did you do to Mu Weijie with this wooden stick?

21
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:36,920
Officer.

22
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:38,920
It wasn't me.

23
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:40,240
I didn't do anything.

24
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,079
Officer,

25
00:02:41,079 --> 00:02:42,240
he just died.

26
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,079
I didn't even

27
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:44,440
touch him.

28
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:49,680
He just died.

29
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:52,600
So you admit it.

30
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:53,360
Come on.

31
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,320
Tell us what happened.

32
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:58,120
I... I

33
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,280
I'll talk.

34
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,160
I'll talk.

35
00:03:02,760 --> 00:03:05,640
Xu Qiaoyue and I have been in a long-distance relationship for a long time.

36
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:08,280
Last week, she suddenly brought up breaking up.

37
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:10,040
She must have someone else.

38
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:13,480
I suspected she hooked up with her art teacher.

39
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,770
So I came to Mancheng immediately.

40
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,640
We had arranged to meet at first,

41
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:20,920
but unexpectedly she stood me up.

42
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:24,200
That afternoon, I called her immediately.

43
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:27,240
I kept calling.

44
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:29,160
I called many times, but she didn't answer.

45
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:31,320
In a fit of anger, I rushed into the studio.

46
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,240
Qiaoyue.

47
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:35,440
Qiaoyue.

48
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:36,880
Who is it?

49
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,640
Who are you looking for?

50
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,560
Get out of the way.

51
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,650
I'm looking for Xu Qiaoyue.

52
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,400
Her class ended early.

53
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,200
She went back.

54
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,440
Bullshit.

55
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:59,160
Don't think I don't know anything.

56
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:01,220
You're the one cuckolding me, right?

57
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,520
What are you talking about?

58
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,520
Get out of the way.

59
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,650
Go back and find her.

60
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,339
What are you doing?

61
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:21,880
Playing dead.

62
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,920
Are you scamming me?

63
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,800
I didn't even hit you.

64
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:30,280
Keep pretending.

65
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,080
Get up.

66
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:37,200
At this time,

67
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,720
Qiaoyue called.

68
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:41,970
She told me she wasn't in the studio at all.

69
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,360
Only then did I know I made a mistake.

70
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:46,040
I was very scared.

71
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,640
So I quickly left that place.

72
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:50,960
Please believe me.

73
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,760
I really didn't kill him.

74
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:55,600
Where were you when you talked on the phone?

75
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,330
I didn't want to see him, so I went home.

76
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,440
Who would have known

77
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:03,810
that such a thing would happen?

78
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:09,440
Then why didn't you call the police afterwards?

79
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:11,400
Allen wouldn't let me call the police.

80
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,600
He checked online

81
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,560
and said

82
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:16,920
that causing death by fright is also punishable.

83
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:19,080
You didn't know he had a heart condition?

84
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,410
Of course I didn't know.

85
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:21,840
You did know.

86
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,440
You used intimidation

87
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:24,600
to trigger his heart attack

88
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,880
and create the illusion of an accidental death.

89
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:27,640
No.

90
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,240
I didn't.

91
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,200
No.

92
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:32,659
Officer, on what grounds do you say that?

93
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:36,120
On the grounds that you cleaned up the scene immediately.

94
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,920
Clean up the scene.

95
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:42,360
If I

96
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,800
cleaned up the scene,

97
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:45,640
No.

98
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,320
If I had cleaned up the scene,

99
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:50,250
I definitely would have wiped my fingerprints clean

100
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:52,480
and put the stick back in its place.

101
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,920
You wouldn't have found any trace of me.

102
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:56,960
Officer,

103
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,480
I am telling the truth.

104
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,200
You are wronging an innocent man!

105
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:01,000
I was wronged!

106
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,080
You said when you went to the studio,

107
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:05,560
you saw Mu Weijie having sex with a woman.

108
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:07,560
Did you see her face clearly?

109
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,120
How would I know?

110
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:13,080
I thought Xu Qiaoyue was inside,

111
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:14,320
so I rushed in.

112
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:17,720
Who knew my girlfriend wasn't even in there.

113
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,680
Then that guy,

114
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,560
he suddenly died.

115
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,360
I got scared and ran away.

116
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:27,960
But officer,

117
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:31,240
