118
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,520
Maybe that guy,

119
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,640
he had some weird kinks.

120
00:06:35,640 --> 00:06:36,280
He found

121
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,600
a prostitute.

122
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,210
Sister Ling,

123
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:43,520
you asked me to verify the alibi of Mu Weijie's wife,

124
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:45,040
Jiang Yifei.

125
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,200
I verified it.

126
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:48,730
She was indeed not in Mancheng that night.

127
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,000
I guessed so.

128
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,720
When she claimed the body,

129
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,850
she showed up dragging a suitcase.

130
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:56,450
It means she had just gotten off the plane.

131
00:06:57,080 --> 00:07:00,540
Then the woman who had sex with him was definitely not his wife.

132
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:01,800
Then who was it?

133
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,040
A prostitute.

134
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:06,040
Could it be that it didn't happen at all?

135
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:08,960
After all, it's just Alan's side of the story.

136
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:10,280
No.

137
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,880
I'm more inclined to believe there is such a person.

138
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,840
The deceased sweated a lot beforehand.

139
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:17,160
It should be caused by strenuous exercise.

140
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,000
Sexual intercourse

141
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,800
fits this characteristic well.

142
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,570
I agree with what Shao said.

143
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:25,800
I also think

144
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:28,480
Alan has no need to make up a woman.

145
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:30,080
The most important thing for us right now

146
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,080
is to find her.

147
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:34,640
But the scene was cleaned up too well.

148
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:36,040
There are no clues at all.

149
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:38,720
There are clues.

150
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:42,840
Exactly because the scene was cleaned up so well,

151
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:45,640
it shows that the woman who was with Mu Weijie

152
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:48,520
is very familiar with the studio.

153
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,680
Familiar with the scene.

154
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:54,080
Then it's either his wife or those female students.

155
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:57,240
Who could it be?

156
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:59,159
We can't interrogate them one by one.

157
00:07:59,159 --> 00:08:00,400
We have no proof,

158
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,730
and they won't admit it.

159
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:04,680
Now that we have a direction for our investigation,

160
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,440
we will find the evidence.

161
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,560
Where is Cheng Mo?

162
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,320
Mr. Cheng

163
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,680
