165
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,560
Buy something?

166
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,800
You said you smelled a pungent scent.

167
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,860
Smell these for me.

168
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,130
Come here and smell.

169
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,760
This one?

170
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:45,720
No.

171
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,730
Smell it carefully.

172
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,520
No.

173
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,370
What about this one?

174
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,480
Officer,

175
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,160
I think

176
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:31,480
