177
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,120
Are you sure?

178
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:37,920
Thank you.

179
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,120
Officer,

180
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,520
I've confessed everything I should. Let me go.

181
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,360
Sit properly.

182
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:45,520
Help!

183
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:46,240
Behave.

184
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:08,840
Why are Xiaobai's legs so short?

185
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,320
Fang.

186
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,520
Hurry outside the art studio

187
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:39,960
and find that parked car.

188
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:42,200
Its dashcam might have captured what happened that day.

189
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,320
Yes, Captain Zhuang.
